node.text:
At first glance, @jesshart's modeling career reads like a fairy-tale success story. But it took the Australian-born model years to realize her true passion. To us, she is unapologetic about admitting that her heart beats more for smoking wheels than for the smoke and mirrors of the fashion world. In our new episode of AMG Uncovered, Jess explains how important it was to overcome the common stereotypes in order to unlock her true self.

Music: 86Tales
